{"article_id":"58c1UttJDgS31wTI","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Phoenix ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"That idea","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that Donald Trump is softening his immigration policy :","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Not going to happen .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The Republican presidential nominee on Wednesday re-upped the harsh immigration rhetoric","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that electrified his primary campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"vowing `` no amnesty '' for undocumented migrants","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"living in the United States","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"and promising to build a `` beautiful '' and `` impenetrable '' border wall","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"that Mexico would pay for","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"-- hours after that country 's president vowed","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that it would n't .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"`` This election is our last chance","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"to secure the border ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"stop illegal immigration ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"and reform our laws","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to make your life better , ''","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Trump said in Phoenix at the end of a dizzying day","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"in which he made his first foray into international diplomacy with a visit to Mexico City ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"then baited a fired-up crowd with red-meat rhetoric .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"On what might have been one of the most important days of his presidential campaign ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Trump appeared to be recommitting his electoral fate in November to the white conservative base voters","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"who swept him to victory in the GOP primary","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"rather than seeking to broaden his base to a wider coalition of Americans .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"adding to the uncertainty","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that has clouded his immigration plan in recent days ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Trump did not give a definitive answer","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"about what he would do with most of the 11 million undocumented people","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who are not criminals ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"leaving open the possibility","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"they would have to continue to hide in the shadows .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"But it was the tone of Trump 's speech","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"that was most notable .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` This is it .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"We wo n't get another opportunity","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"-- it will be too late , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he said in a speech","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that recreated the vision of a dystopian , crime-riddled nation on the edge of an existential crisis","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that he deployed in his convention speech in Cleveland in July .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"He vowed to create a `` deportation task force '' within the Immigration and Customs Enforcement division `` focused on identifying and quickly removing the most dangerous criminal illegal aliens in America . ''","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"he would boost the ranks of enforcement agents","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"to enforce existing laws .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"He vowed","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that any undocumented immigrants","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"who are caught crossing into the US","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"will be `` detained","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"until they are removed from our country ''","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"and sent back to their country of origin .","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"And he promised to repeal President Barack Obama 's executive orders","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"shielding some younger undocumented people ,","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"including those","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"born in the United States","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"-- so called Dreamers ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"from deportation .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Trump left the fate of most of the 11 million undocumented people","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"who are not criminals in the country","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"murky .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"He did not commit to deporting every undocumented immigrant","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"living in the US","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"as he previously had ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"but vowed","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"that immigrants","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"living in the US illegally","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"would never have a path to legal status under his presidency .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"`` For those here today illegally","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"who are seeking legal status ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"they will have one route and only one route :","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"to return home","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and apply for re-entry under the rules of the new legal immigration system . ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Dad :","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"If Trump had been president ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"my son would be alive","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"MUST WATCH Dad :","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"If Trump had been president ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"my son would be alive","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"05:47","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"But later , Trump said","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"once a new immigration system is in place ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"`` we will be in a position","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to consider the appropriate disposition of those","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"who remain . ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"In his speech , the billionaire repeatedly called attention to the crimes of some undocumented immigrants","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"and drew on stories of Americans","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"killed by undocumented immigrants ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"bringing parents of some of those victims on stage","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"to share their graphic and heart-wrenching tales of loss .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Consistent with the law-and-order theme","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"he has emphasized ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Trump vowed a `` zero tolerance '' policy toward criminals","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"living in the US illegally .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"As he painted a picture of a country","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"besieged by `` illegal alien '' crime ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Trump accused Washington politicians and the media of underplaying the dangers","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"posed by illegal immigration","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"and warned voters","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"that the stakes this election will never be higher .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"`` If we can save American lives , American jobs and American futures , together","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"we can save America itself , ''","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Trump 's hard-line speech contrasted strikingly with his more moderate tone in Mexico City hours earlier","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"when he put on a restrained and respectful performance ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"even as he publicly disagreed with President Enrique Peña Nieto ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"who had invited him and Democratic nominee Hillary Clinton to Mexico for talks .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"Donald Trump :","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"We will end 'sanctuary cities '","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Donald Trump :","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"We will end 'sanctuary cities '","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"02:02","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"The visit was an apparent attempt","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"to portray Trump in a statesmanlike light","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"and to counter Clinton 's claims","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that he is temperamentally unfit to be President .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Trump 's campaign will likely be pleased","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that he got a photo-op with a foreign leader","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"and appeared to avoid any damaging gaffes","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"as he stood soberly on stage , beside an interpreter .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"But the risks of such a visit","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"-- Trump 's first official encounter with a foreign leader --","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"were underscored","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"when the stagecraft began to unravel over the issue of the wall on the Mexican border .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Trump had told reporters","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"that he and his host did not discuss the cost","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"of who would pay for the multibillion-dollar project","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"-- a statement","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"that the Mexican president did not contest","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"while alongside Trump .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"But he quickly said on Twitter","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"that the wall came up ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and there was no way","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"Mexico would be paying .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"`` At the start of the conversation with Donald Trump , I made it clear","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"that Mexico will not pay for the wall , ''","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Peña Nieto tweeted .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"The confusion and apparent contradiction between the two men was quickly seized upon by the Clinton campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"which mocked Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"the disconnect undercut his image as a great dealmaker .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"`` Trump just failed his first foreign test .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"Diplomacy is n't as easy","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"as it looks .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"-- H '' Clinton said in a personally signed Tweet .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"Trump just failed his first foreign test .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"Diplomacy is n't as easy","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"as it looks .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"-H","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"- Hillary Clinton","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"( @ HillaryClinton )","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"September 1 , 2016","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"Jason Miller , Trump 's senior communications adviser , called the meeting `` the first part of the discussion and a relationship builder '' between the two men .","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"`` It was not a negotiation ,","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"and that would have been inappropriate .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"It is unsurprising that they hold two different views on this issue ,","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"and we look forward to continuing the conversation , ''","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"Miller said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"Peña Nieto twice stressed the `` responsibility ''","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"he has","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"to defend Mexican people around the world","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"Trump has made `` assertions","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"that regrettably had hurt and have affected Mexicans . ''","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"`` The Mexican people have felt hurt by the comments","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that have been made .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"But I am sure","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"that his genuine interest is to build a relationship","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that will give both of our societies better welfare , ''","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"Peña Nieto said .","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"The Clinton campaign also argued","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"that Trump 's performance in Mexico proved","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"that his tough guy image was just an act .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"`` Donald Trump has made his outlandish policy","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"of forcing Mexico to pay for his giant wall the centerpiece of his campaign .","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"But at the first opportunity","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"to make good on his offensive campaign promises ,","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"Trump choked , ''","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"Clinton campaign chairman John Podesta said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"`` What we saw today from a man","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"who claims to be the ultimate 'deal maker '","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"is that he does n't have the courage","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"to advocate for his campaign promises","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"when he 's not in front of a friendly crowd , ''","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"Podesta said ,","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"before accusing Trump of wanting to build a costly wall at American taxpayers ' expense .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"Podesta later added :","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"`` It turns out Trump did n't just choke ,","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"he got beat in the room","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"and lied about it . ''","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"But Trump was adamant in his speech in Arizona","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"that Mexico would indeed finance the wall","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"if he becomes President .","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"`` Mexico will pay for the wall .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"100 percent , ''","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"`` They do n't know it yet ,","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"but they are going to pay for the wall . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":403,"left":0,"right":402,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":402,"left":308,"right":401,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":308,"left":256,"right":307,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":204,"right":255,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":255,"left":219,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":211,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":205,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":206,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":207,"right":208,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":215,"right":217,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":12,"right":214,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":13,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":213,"left":14,"right":212,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":17,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":222,"right":253,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":222,"left":20,"right":221,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":221,"left":220,"right":23,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":21,"right